impress.js  is a library that lets the users  create interactive presentations
It's based on the power of the  CSS3 in the  modern browsers
But there is a problem with all of this cool stuff
This presentations are HTML documents which creating is not easy ... and this is a problem
Creating of this presentations is slow and this is the reason for building...

What is JSpres?
JSpres goals
